pages.policy: Elite Office Creations | Privacy policy Estate Elite Experts Home Catalog About us Contact us Privacy Policy At Estate Elite Experts, we take your privacy and the security of your personal information very seriously. Use of Personal Information: We use the personal information collected to provide you with real estate services and to communicate with you about properties, promotions, and other relevant information related to our business. Disclosure of Personal Information: We may disclose your personal information to third parties such as escrow companies, mortgage lenders, and other real estate professionals to facilitate the buying or selling of properties or to provide you with requested services. Protection of Personal Information: We take measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. We use secure servers and encryption technology to safeguard your data. Retention of Personal Information: We retain your personal information as long as necessary for the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, or as required by law. Your Rights: You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information held by us. You may also opt out of receiving marketing communications from us at any time. Changes to Privacy Policy: We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on our website, and we encourage you to review this Policy periodically. Contact Us: If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or the handling of your personal information, please contact us at estateeliteexperts@gmail.com. By using our services or visiting our website, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. Thank you for trusting Estate Elite Experts with your real estate needs.
